<inglise> Intra-day credits by the European Central Bank or the national banks to the public sector shall not be considered as a credit facility within the meaning of Article 104 of the Treaty, provided that they remain limited to the day and that no extension is possible. </inglise>
<eesti> Euroopa Keskpanga v&otilde;i keskpankade p&auml;evasiseseid laene avalikule sektorile ei loeta laenuv&otilde;imaluseks asutamislepingu artikli 104 t&auml;henduses tingimusel, et need piirnevad p&auml;evaga ning neid ei saa pikendada. </eesti>
